{"tid":652224,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[痴撚左線同一個台開3個]90's Telegram Group","createTime":"2018-05-03T16:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T14:15:19.000Z","uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f6e57dd6b61550e254f8b935c63af45487e8ef7d","tid":652224,"uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T16:35:43.000Z","msg":"開左個TG Group. 有私隱得來其實都唔係話勁有私隱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎90後各行各業嘅各位一齊入來吹下水傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我們希望關系和諧，因始沒有你我之分，更沒有兩登之分<br />\n<br />\n90's Telegram Group為會員而設，暫時只限相關會員加入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGroup內比較著重繁體字及廣東話文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果對呢方面保有獨特嘅執著請勿申請<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩填一填表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n表格會開到5月9日，填妥表格後會收到一封確認電郵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n收集左各位巴打反映表格收集太多個人資料，所以已經進行簡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但部份保障措施必不可少：同意所有條款後會需求輸入電話號號作收取入Group連結用途，此舉係希望確保表格均為本人有填寫及意識下同意條款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScdlZMWvaXQT6lNdjFwVzjE629Dx4gpTbyt7cgZnpkc2FqfWg/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScdlZMWvaXQT6lNdjFwVzjE629Dx4gpTbyt7cgZnpkc2FqfWg%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=IwZ7%2FQfOGqH3UTmK1RqLEJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9a7224d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScdlZMWvaXQT6lNdjFwVzjE629Dx4gpTbyt7cgZnpkc2FqfWg/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n香港好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望大家傾計傾得開心又放心"},{"pid":"2acf4d2e0d38d68a454457f392a09202aacb1bc9","tid":652224,"uid":103339,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T16:4